## Calculating the Fs in 2-way ANOVA



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
tribble(
~Source, ~SS, ~df, ~MS, ~F,
"Coffee",432, "","","",
"Dark",486,"","","",
"Coffee x Dark",540,"","","",
"Error",5184,"","",""
) |> 
  gt() |> 
    cols_align(align = "center",
             columns = SS:F)
```

